collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (28 total Queries, 28 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `wa`.`id`, `wa`.`package`, COUNT(DISTINCT cs.id) AS total_cs, COUNT(DISTINCT web.id) AS total_web, IFNULL(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT cs.cs_number ORDER BY cs.cs_number SEPARATOR ', '), '-') AS details_cs, IFNULL(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT web.url ORDER BY web.url SEPARATOR ', '), '-') AS details_web, `wa`.`date_created`, `wa`.`custom_name`, `wa`.`rotator_mode`, `jasa`.`order_client_reff` FROM `table_order_wa_chat_rotator` as `wa` LEFT JOIN `table_cs_wa_chat_rotator` as `cs` ON `wa`.`id` = `cs`.`order_id` LEFT JOIN `table_web_wa_chat_rotator` as `web` ON `wa`.`id` = `web`.`order_id` LEFT JOIN `table_order_jasa` as `jasa` ON `jasa`.`order_id` = `wa`.`id` AND `order_type`='wa_chat_rotator' GROUP BY `wa`.`id`, `wa`.`package`, `wa`.`date_created` ORDER BY `wa`.`id`

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT `wa`.`id`, `wa`.`package`, COUNT(DISTINCT cs.id) AS total_cs, COUNT(DISTINCT web.id) AS total_web, IFNULL(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT cs.cs_number ORDER BY cs.cs_number SEPARATOR ', '), '-') AS details_cs, IFNULL(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT web.url ORDER BY web.url SEPARATOR ', '), '-') AS details_web, `wa`.`date_created`, `wa`.`custom_name`, `wa`.`rotator_mode`, `jasa`.`order_client_reff` FROM `table_order_wa_chat_rotator` as `wa` LEFT JOIN `table_cs_wa_chat_rotator` as `cs` ON `wa`.`id` = `cs`.`order_id` LEFT JOIN `table_web_wa_chat_rotator` as `web` ON `wa`.`id` = `web`.`order_id` LEFT JOIN `table_order_jasa` as `jasa` ON `jasa`.`order_id` = `wa`.`id` AND `order_type`='wa_chat_rotator' GROUP BY `wa`.`id`, `wa`.`package`, `wa`.`date_created` ORDER BY `wa`.`id`
